Subject: [PATCH] meta-amd:dbus:Cpu Add vendor ID

Add vendor ID property to Cpu interface.
set type of vendor ID to string.

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: Abinaya Dhandapani <abinaya.dhandapani@amd.com>
---
 yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/Inventory/Item/Cpu.interface.yaml | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/Inventory/Item/Cpu.interface.yaml b/yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/Inventory/Item/Cpu.interface.yaml
index c134417..17842b1 100644
--- a/yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/Inventory/Item/Cpu.interface.yaml
+++ b/yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/Inventory/Item/Cpu.interface.yaml
@@ -61,6 +61,10 @@ properties:
       description: >
           The microcode information for this processor
       default: 0
+    - name: VendorId
+      type: string
+      description: >
+          The vendor identification for this processor.

 enumerations:
     - name: Capability
